The addition of an Event field in Person requires several changes to other classes.

As a first step towards integrating this field, let's add the event field as an argument to several methods.
Refactor Search and Edit command names

Currently, there is no way to associate people with events.

Let's create a PersonEventManager class that will handle the
association of people to events.

We can also make several changes to the ModelManager
to facilitate this change.
Fix some minor bugs which were missed in prior PR

To facilitate linking people to events, let's add a new link command
as well as the relevant parser for it.

Update the Model class as well to handle the implementation
of these classes.

Sync up local branch to be in line with the team repo.

This will fix the check issues
